| Storage Account (source) | ushacloudmigrationpoc | West US 2 | Active |
| Storage Account (NCUS) | ushacloudmigrationncus | North Central US | Active |
| VHD Blob | Node5_Fixed_Final.vhd | North Central US | Copied — success |
| Managed Disk | disk-node5-os-ncus | North Central US | Attached to VM |
