- Created OLE DB Connection Manager — Node5.CoreBank_OnPrem_POC using Windows Authentication

- Tested connection — succeeded

- Added Data Flow Task to Control Flow canvas

- Inside Data Flow: added OLE DB Source — selected [Banking].[Transactions] table

- Previewed data — confirmed TransactionID, AccountID, TransactionDate, TransactionType, Amount columns

- Added Flat File Destination — created new connection manager CoreBank_Transactions_Output

- Output file: C:\SSIS_Output\CoreBank_Transactions.csv — Delimited format, column names in first row

