# **K.7 Complete POC Build — End to End Reference**

This section documents the complete ADF POC build from infrastructure through Gold layer in simple sequential format. All steps were completed and validated on 3/31/2026 with a full all-green pipeline run.

## **K.7.1 Phase 1 — Azure Infrastructure**

**Resource Group**

