## **K.8.8 ADF — Databricks Integration**

Date: March 31, 2026. This phase wires ADF to trigger the Gold_Analysis Databricks notebook as the final stage of the PL_CoreBank_SSIS_To_ADLS pipeline. After DF_SilverToGold completes and gold_transactions.parquet is confirmed in ADLS Gen2, ADF calls the Databricks REST API to submit a notebook job run, polls for completion, and surfaces the result in ADF Monitor.

