Author → Pipelines → PL_CoreBank_SSIS_To_ADLS. Expanded Databricks section in Activities panel. Dragged Notebook activity onto canvas to the right of DF_SilverToGold. ADF auto-connected the success path arrow from DF_SilverToGold → Notebook activity.

